      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ハッピーメリークリスマス！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Merry Christmas!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 3.1711337326000004,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_xmasstage-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 3.3844670134
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_04-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "みなさんこんばんは！\n今日はクリスマスライブに来てくれてありがとう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good evening‚ everyone.\nThank you for coming to our Christmas show today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.3844670134,
      "endTime": 8.3344671087,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_xmasstage-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 8.5478005566
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_04-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "じゃーん！\n見て見て！　この衣装、すっごく可愛いよね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ta-dah!\nLook at this! Isn’t this costume just so cute?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.5478005566,
      "endTime": 14.444433333300001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_xmasstage-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 14.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_04-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "よう似合っとるわ\nやっぱりクリスマスといえばサンタコスプレやな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It really suits you.\nChristmas is the time for cosplay as Santa.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.6333333333,
      "endTime": 20.1712774424,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_xmasstage-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 20.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_04-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "コスプレじゃなくてステージ衣装！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s not cosplay‚ these are our stage costumes!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.3666666667,
      "endTime": 23.2043310802,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_xmasstage-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 23.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_04-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "今夜は私達がサンタになって\nみなさんに楽しいクリスマスをお届けします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Tonight we’re going to be Santas‚\nand deliver a fun Christmas to everyone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.4,
      "endTime": 29.2943792173,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_xmasstage-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 29.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_04-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "会場に集まってくれたみんなに\n沢山のドキドキをプレゼントするね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’ll give everyone here the gift of\nan exciting show!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.5,
      "endTime": 34.604284954200004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_xmasstage-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 34.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_04-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "TRINITYAiLEのクリスマスライブ\n一曲目は新曲、『lumière』！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The TRINITYAiLE Christmas live!\nThe first song is our new one‚ “Lumière”!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.7666666667,
      "endTime": 40.2756425434,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1566.6666667000015
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_xmasvenue-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 41.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_04-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "ふう……。イベント、無事に終わったなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Phew… The event went off without a hitch.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.5333333333,
      "endTime": 46.4508617719,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_04-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "今日のライブ、凄い盛り上がりだったね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Today’s show got super lively.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.6333333333,
      "endTime": 49.9241270383,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_xmasvenue-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 50.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_04-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "クリスマスツリーにイルミネーション……\n綺麗な景色の中で歌うのは楽しかったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Christmas trees all lit up…\nIt was fun to sing in such pretty scenery.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.1333333333,
      "endTime": 55.805945942499996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_xmasvenue-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 55.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_04-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "真冬の野外ライブなのに\nお客さんの熱気で寒さも吹き飛んじゃったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even though we got live outside in midwinter‚\nthe fans’ enthusiasm blew the cold away.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.9666666667,
      "endTime": 61.5221709855,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_xmasvenue-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 61.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_04-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "クリスマスライブ大成功やね\nほんまに楽しかったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The Christmas show was a great success.\nIt really was fun.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.7333333333,
      "endTime": 66.89999999999999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_xmasvenue-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 67.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_04-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "急に決まったイベントだったけど\nファンのみんなも喜んでくれて、やって良かったわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was decided at the last minute‚\nbut the fans were so happy‚ I’m glad we did it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.1666666667,
      "endTime": 72.8038722413,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_xmasvenue-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 73
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_04-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "うん、そうだね\nみんなに楽しんでもらえて、やって良かったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ that’s true.\nIt’s good that we could give everyone a good time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73,
      "endTime": 78.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_xmasvenue-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 78.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_04-smr009.m4a",
      "text": "あ、私は{user}さんに用事があるから\n二人は先に楽屋に戻っててくれる？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ I’ve got an errand for {user}-san‚ so\nyou two should go ahead back to the dressing rooms.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.9666666667,
      "endTime": 85.2568404397,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_xmasvenue-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 85.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_04-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "分かったわ。それじゃ、先に行ってるから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Got it. Okay‚ we’re going ahead.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.4333333333,
      "endTime": 88.3735375245,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_04-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "ほな、また後でな～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "See you later~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.5666666667,
      "endTime": 91.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 90.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_xmasvenue-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 92.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_04-smr010.m4a",
      "text": "うん、また後でね\n用事が済んだら私もすぐに行くから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ later.\nI’ll be there as soon as I’m done.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.0333333333,
      "endTime": 97.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_xmasvenue-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 97.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_04-smr011.m4a",
      "text": "……って、本当はプレゼントを取りに行くんだけどね\n二人とも喜んでくれるといいな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…But really‚ I’m going to get the presents.\nI hope they’ll like it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.6333333333,
      "endTime": 105.7016123512,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5100.000000000008
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_xmasvenue-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 102.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 106.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_04-smr012.m4a",
      "text": "お待たせー！　遅くなってごめんね\nあれ？　二人とももう着替えたの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry I’m late! Thanks for waiting.\nHuh? You’re both changed already?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.8333333333,
      "endTime": 114.7261904954,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 114.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_04-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "ごめんなさい\n急な仕事で私と優はすぐ行かなきゃいけなくなったの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry.\nWe got an urgent job‚ so Yu-chan and I have to go ahead.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.9333333333,
      "endTime": 120.4320727285,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 120.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
